Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分開了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.63,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這座山因為被邪惡帝皇\N多惡達支配了的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連彩虹的顏色也變成了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、火美子和武一郎師傅\N一邊與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.81,0:01:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於上到了第三界層了\N原本第三界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.32,0:01:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由支配寒冷的極寒之劍\N與支配炎熱的灼熱之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令這處的氣溫剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.56,0:02:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是多惡達用灼熱之劍\N換了極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令第三界層變成了個\N熱得不得了的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要令這個世界恢復原本的氣溫\N便一定要找出極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們終於知道了\N它竟在第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.64,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和龍神丸、火美子、師傅\N分離上到了第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五話\N喚醒吧!火龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.30,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛了多惡達大人\N是不會就此算數的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.30,0:03:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢呢\N火美子和百人僊人沒問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你認為怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能會沒問題吧?\N我的立場到底會變成怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從剛才起\N便一直在自言自語什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔!\N回來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,只有你一人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡上了第四界層啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?第四界層?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說一定會\N把極寒之劍帶回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了!不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生\N不是不行了,是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,百人僊人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失了?怎麼回事?\N我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢欺騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?什麼意思?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太丟臉了,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古…古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?一定要處理你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷…\N這裏便是第四界層嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和第三界層完全相反呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點找出極寒之劍\N會死在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!龍神丸呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,是用盡了能量嗎?\N要怎樣才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,去找火龍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍?我明白了\N總之找到火龍便可以了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.87,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天定會捉到你\N讓你知道抵抗是沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會讓你接近洞穴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪珠!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來,小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無用的反抗!無用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去了,停啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已說了那是無用的反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那邊有沒有什麼事發生?\N東傑何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,多多高麾大人\N這麼精神真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢!我收到聯絡\N渡已上了這個第四界層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是玩的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是剛才的傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東傑何狄,我們在此收拾渡\N天下便是我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我們\N便可以支配更高的界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以成為\N多惡達大人的左右手,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,我現在立刻開始追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看來不像是\N多惡達的手下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.15,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫雪,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個,是名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了找極寒之劍\N從第三界層來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒之劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在在找火龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的背叛者\N知道厲害了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有背叛啊,所也所也\N請你多給我一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉嗦!\N現在的你可以做到什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴你一個好消息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.08,0:08:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在殘酷大人、殘惡鳥大人\N殘豹大人快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔…魔界三兄弟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,是多惡達大人\N命令他們來殺了你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開門啊!竟困我在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.91,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們以為在下是誰啊?\N在下是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河馬啊!\N是啊!喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果拿到那傢伙的鑰匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我去取回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以離開這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼不早說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又沒有問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,快去取吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,開鎖之術\N出門之前不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要靜靜的去啊,靜靜的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靜靜的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[殘豹]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[殘惡鳥]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[殘酷]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是我的故鄉\N高千高千市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高千高千市?\N火龍在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏怎麼了?大家也冰封了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣的?\N這是突然發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天忽然有團黑霧\N來到這裏上空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.62,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我因拿著爺爺給我的遺物\N火龍的鱗片才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍的鱗片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在龍之洞穴的火龍\N是火炎之龍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要拿著這鱗片\N便不會冰封了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它住在龍之洞穴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然火龍也許能\N令這市鎮恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是支配著這裏的\N東傑何狄阻擋我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我不能接近洞穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去龍之洞穴吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令市鎮恢復原狀\N也許會知道極寒之劍在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘…殘酷將軍,請原諒我\N請你給多一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.40,0:12:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!以為有事\N可以求得動殘兄弟大人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥,不如把這背叛者\N燒了來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊,會吃壞肚子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥,我已很膩了\N還是快殺了他走人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也\N夠了,快了結他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請…請等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿矛來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你覺悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請…請停手\N所也所也,再給多一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.68,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也\N這傢伙的命暫時交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還有點利用價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.42,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下去收拾他們\N你在這裏等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,趁現在快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,要救鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢\N可是不知道他被困在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鳥先生的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪邊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了!辛苦你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏嗎?\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N你再用多次剛才的開鎖術吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧,我現在來救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…是來救我的嗎?\N為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊?\N我們不是同伴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同伴啊!同伴啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同…同伴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這藥是忍部一族\N代代相傳的萬能藥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塗了這個的話\N不論什麼傷也會很快復原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為何只有古拿瑪一個\N要受這些苦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…因為我知道很多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的父親也是什麼也知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這藥的製法\N也是父親教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有父親的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在在哪裏?\N不知所蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不知所蹤?\N怎會這樣的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他去了收拾多惡達\N但沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個的另一半是我父親拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?看來好像什麼痛苦\N也沒有的長大的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來也有這麼痛苦的過去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受了傷的時候\N父親也是這樣子摸我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N今天眼睛特別多汗流出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣,你經常用笑臉\N來隱藏和父親分離的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下最怕聽這種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子你放心吧\N在下一定會幫你找出你父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前\N你便當我是你的父親吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的父親\N是比你好很多的男人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你暫時忍耐一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.12,0:16:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說客氣話了\N走吧,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.32,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這裏嗎?\N如果是火龍住不是太冷了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但的確應該是這裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條不是火龍而是冰龍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它向這邊來了,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無用的反抗也到此為止了\N渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是東傑何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍已被多惡達大人\N變成冰龍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是無用的反抗呢\N辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.80,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.80,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,它已不能變回火龍了嗎\N鎮內的人也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是沒辦法\N只要除掉那金頸環便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.90,0:17:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這也是無用的反抗\N這是絕對不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗有分什麼有用無用嗎?\N戰鬥也有分戰了也沒改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰…總之只有試試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.86,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰龍\N把那傲慢的小鬼變成冰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有干了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.94,0:17:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已說了這是無用的反抗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.00,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再做無用的反抗了\N一起看渡被冰封吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,龍神丸不能動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,火龍的鱗片!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.82,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會變冰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,把鱗片投出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.95,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,甦醒吧!火龍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.29,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,這不是無用的反抗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼便用魔神決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍\N請你令雪的市鎮恢復原狀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍,謝謝你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼\N我要把你打得體無完膚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無用的反抗!無用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.28,0:20:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.12,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!\N渡,你做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又在做無用的反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,用飛龍拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.75,0:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是無用的反抗啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.31,0:21:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,謝謝你從多惡達的咒縛中\N把我解放出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.60,0:21:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍,可以告訴我極寒之劍\N在哪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道極寒之劍在哪裏\N但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.36,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,接著去北面的野野谷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會有極寒之劍的線索的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野野谷?雪,你認識路嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.39,0:22:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你可以帶我去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.87,0:22:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!出發吧\N目的地是野野谷!

